// DiagramEmbed
// AI-UI component that renders a named diagram from the session inside a chat
// message. Looks up the diagram by name from the session store and passes its
// content to MermaidPreview.

FUNCTION DiagramEmbed(diagramName, height) -> JSX                      EXPORT
  CALLS: MermaidPreview (MermaidPreview)
  Reads diagrams from sessionStore. Finds the diagram matching diagramName.
  IF not found: shows "Diagram not found" placeholder.
  ELSE: renders MermaidPreview with the diagram content and fixed height.
